        "Career statistics": "As of 3 June 2024",
        "International career": "Between 2014 and 2021, Celar played for all Slovenian youth teams from under-16 to under-21, making 46 appearances for all teams combined and scoring 17 goals.On 14 November 2021, Celar debuted for the senior team in a World Cup qualifying match against Cyprus."
